Reveal 1 monster in your hand that has 1000 DEF and either 2400 or 2800 ATK; add 1 "Monarchs" Spell/Trap Card or 1 "The First Monarch" from your Deck to your hand, except "Grudge of the Monarchs". You can only activate 1 "Grudge of the Monarchs" per turn.
